Notes:

live-server and nodmon keeps track of the changes
transpiler - transforms source code (es6) into target language(es5).
Stateless functional components = constant function, one that will always return the same component(e.g. HTML).  Will not have any methods.
Stateful component(class) - one that is dynamic and can change.



